improved_metadata.title: Spray It Loud (DJ Foam Bob's Energy Saving Anthem)
improved_metadata.description: A high-energy electronic track promoting 'Spray phone,' a product apparently related to insulation and energy savings. DJ Foam Bob urges listeners to 'spray it loud, spray it proud' for a cooler and more energy-efficient home.
improved_metadata.key_lyrics: Spray it loud, spray it proud
